name: Alone To Nature - Demo
description:
The Wendigo, Puzzles, and Sandbox Horror Survival!

 What more could you love about it? 

  • Explore New Realms
  • Solve Puzzles
  • Fight Your Way Threw The Night

Welcome to my first game, and solo indie project. This game is a heavy work in progress, but I'm putting my all into it. If you enjoy the demo and would like to contribute in anyway feel free to leave a donation or even reach out!

my email is "theboifanta@gmail.com" and my inbox is always open to anyone interested in helping in any way.

 Have an idea or just notice a bug?

Contact me by email, and give me a solid description of the issue as well as screenshots if possible.
